title: Faience fragment of cartouche

The arrow on both sides of the drawing indicates that the object is upside down. The hieroglyphs in the cartouche read: 'Aten' (itn); and below the cartouche 'eternity' (nhh).
There is a comment below the title but it is difficult to read: 'Aten name where I have representations'?
